{
 "name": "RPlog_Turning_Solo_Over_to_the_Empire",
 "title": "Turning Solo Over to the Empire",
 "summary": "On the CSA capital world of Etti IV, the Authority official Simone Drake--eager to be rid of the New Republic warships menacing her sector--escorts the cloaked Imperial agent Sabbath to the Port Security Office where Han Solo is being held prisoner. Sabbath gloats over the captured smuggler, who responds with characteristic defiance and a failed escape attempt, before Sabbath subdues him with a brutal choke and a drugged vial that knocks him unconscious. Hoisting Solo over his shoulders, Sabbath carries him across the late-night starport to his shuttle, the Crazy Diamond, and departs for Imperial space, thanking Drake for her cooperation. Drake, anxious to keep the handover quiet, returns home through the city, passing--without recognizing--the disguised musician Shenner playing flute on a park bench, who is shaken to realize how close she has come to the dangerous woman's residence.",
